OL,3,CMan, 37, dies following 'medical
OL,4,Cepisode' in custody
OL,6,FA man who was being held in police
OL,7,Fcustody in Swindon has died.
OL,9,FWiltshire Police confirmed Piotr Rak,
OL,10,F37, died on Sunday 19 May at
OL,11,FGablecross Police Station in Swindon.
OL,13,FThe force confirmed that Mr Rak was
OL,14,Farrested in the early hours of 18 May
OL,15,Fon Fleet Street in the town on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of being drunk while in his
OL,17,Fcar.
