OL,3,CMan, 37, dies following 'medical
OL,4,Cepisode' in custody
OL,6,F"We understand Mr Rak was seen by
OL,7,Fpolice getting into the car which was
OL,8,Fstationary when officers approached",
OL,9,Fa spokesperson said.
OL,11,FThey went on to say Mr Rak provided a
OL,12,Fpositive breath test at the scene.
OL,14,FHe was then taken to Gablecross Police
OL,15,FStation around an hour after his
OL,16,Farrest and Mr Rak was placed on
OL,17,Fregular observations by staff,
OL,18,Faccording to the force.
