OL,3,CMan, 37, dies following 'medical
OL,4,Cepisode' in custody
OL,6,FIt was shortly after 8am on Sunday 19
OL,7,FMay that he was found to be
OL,8,Fexperiencing a medical episode.
OL,10,FCPR was started and an ambulance and
OL,11,Femergency helicopter arrived soon
OL,12,Fafter.
OL,14,FMr Rak was pronounced dead at the
OL,15,Fpolice station at 9am that morning.
OL,17,FThe force has referred itself to the
OL,18,FOffice of Police Conduct (IOPC)
OL,19,Ffollowing the death.
