OL,3,CMan, 37, dies following 'medical
OL,4,Cepisode' in custody
OL,6,FIOPC regional director Derrick
OL,7,FCampbell said: "I send my sincere
OL,8,Fcondolences to the family and friends
OL,9,Fof Mr Rak for their sad loss.
OL,11,F"We have now met Mr Rak's family and
OL,12,Fexplained our role and how our
OL,13,Finvestigation will progress.
OL,15,F"We will be examining police actions
OL,16,Fin taking Mr Rak into custody and the
OL,17,Flevel of care provided to him over the
OL,18,Faround 30 hour period he was detained.
