OL,6,F"We are independent of the police and
OL,7,Fit is important that we carry out an
OL,8,Finvestigation to fully establish the
OL,9,Fcircumstances when someone has died in
OL,10,Fpolice custody."
OL,12,F"We will also be viewing CCTV from the
OL,13,Fcustody suite and body worn video from
OL,14,Fofficers who took part in Mr Rak's
OL,15,Farrest", he added.
